(65443, -1, 'options_options_enableaccess_text', 'cphelptext', 'Access masks allow you to enable or disable access to a particular forum for individual user(s). To use them, you must enable this option. This option also affects whether or not users will be able to see forums they do not have access to on forumhome and forumdisplay. (If this is off, they will see them in forum listings but not be able to enter them. If this is on, they will not see them at all.)', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
