(62147, -1, 'vbblog_faq_reading_and_posting_how_do_i_post', 'faqtext', '<p>If you are allowed to post blog entries, you will always have a link at the top of the blog sidebar titled "Add new Post".  This link allows you to post entries immediately, entries that will post automatically at a future date, or create a draft entry for later review and posting.</p>', 'vbblog', 'Wayne Luke', 1260378722, '4.0.0 Release Candidate 2', 0),
(62146, -1, 'vbblog_faq_reading_and_posting_categories', 'faqtext', '<p>You may categorize entries in multiple categories of your own creation.  Before you may categorize entries, you must define your categories in the <span class="smallfont" style="font-weight: bold">Blog Control Panel</span>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After creating your categories, you will be able to select multiple categories from the blog entry page during the creation of a new entry, or by editing an existing entry.</p>', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1188343323, '1.0.0', 0),
(62145, -1, 'vbblog_faq_reading_and_posting', 'faqtext', '', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1188333149, '1.0.0', 0),
(62144, -1, 'vbblog_faq_groups_what', 'faqtext', 'A Group Blog is a blog made up of entries from several contributors or authors. This is a good way to have a single blog with contributions from all of your staff.', 'vbblog', 'Wayne Luke', 1260377860, '4.0.0 Release Candidate 2', 0),
(62142, -1, 'vbblog_faq_groups', 'faqtext', '', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1216670894, '2.0.0 Beta 1', 0),
(62143, -1, 'vbblog_faq_groups_join', 'faqtext', 'You must be invited by the blog owner in order to join a blog.', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1216670999, '2.0.0 Beta 1', 0),
(62140, -1, 'vbblog_faq_general_sidebar', 'faqtext', '<p>The blog sidebar contains the links to maintain your blog as well as information in regards to your blog and the other blogs that you may visit.</p>', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1188340004, '1.0.0', 0),
(62141, -1, 'vbblog_faq_general_what', 'faqtext', '<p>Wikipedia defines a blog as:<br />\r\nA blog is a type of website, usually maintained by an individual with regular entries of commentary, descriptions of events, or other material such as graphics or video. Entries are commonly displayed in reverse-chronological order. "Blog" can also be used as a verb, meaning to maintain or add content to a blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On this site, a blog is your own personal space to write about your topics and share them with other community members.</p>', 'vbblog', 'Wayne Luke', 1260378448, '4.0.0 Release Candidate 2', 0),
(62136, -1, 'you_do_not_have_permission_to_view_category', 'error', 'You do not have permission to view a category that one of your chosen items belongs to.', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1208291090, '2.0.0 Beta 1', 0),
(62137, -1, 'vbblog_faq', 'faqtext', 'The Blog system gives you your own personal space at $vboptions[bbtitle]. Depending on how the administrator has configured the blog, you will be able to create your own entries and control who may view them.', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1188332512, '1.0.0', 0),
(62138, -1, 'vbblog_faq_general', 'faqtext', '', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1188332871, '1.0.0', 0),
(62139, -1, 'vbblog_faq_general_customsidebar', 'faqtext', 'Yes, you can customize the sidebar. With the customization you can rearrange the order of blocks and create your own custom blocks for additional content. To customize your sidebar click on "Blog Settings" in the navigation bar and then select "Organize Sidebar."', 'vbblog', 'Wayne Luke', 1260378648, '4.0.0 Release Candidate 2', 0),
