(63295, -1, 'cms_articles_preview', 'faqtext', '<p>vBulletin allows you to create a special access section that only a select group of users can view.  Users who are not in the group can''t normally view the articles in the section. But, when the preview option is selected, it allows these users to get a sneak peak of the article. </p>\r\n<div style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:4px;border:0;"><img src="images/help/article_preview.png" height="387" width="769" alt="Article Preview" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>NOTE: The preview option must be selected in the section options as well.</p>', 'vbcms', 'Wayne Luke', 1269014047, '4.1.0 Beta 1', 0),
