(63245, -1, 'options_options_cms_preview_thumb_text', 'cphelptext', 'If set, this will cause the CMS to use the stored thumbnail for any article preview images that are local attachments. Preview images that are not local attachments will not be affected. Note that both thumbnail creation and the display of thumbnails must be enabled (in the message attachment options) for this setting to have any effect.', 'vbcms', 'Paul', 1325026716, '4.1.10 Alpha 2', 0),
