(61593, -1, 'setting_glowhostspamomatic_result_timeout_desc', 'vbsettings', 'What should happen if the remote connection times out when querying the new registration?<br><br><i>* Note: Only applies if set to block listed registrations in the above setting</i>', 'glowhostspamomatic', 'glowhostspamomatic', 1280241504, '1.0.0', 0),
