(61842, -1, 'options_options_vbblog_tagcloud_tags_text', 'cphelptext', 'The maximum number of tags that will be displayed in the tag cloud. A higher number provides more information to a user but may appear to be more cluttered.', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1231202059, '2.0.1', 0),
