(64905, -1, 'language_files_just_phrases_text', 'cphelptext', 'By "language settings" we mean the settings you see when you click the [Edit Settings] link in the <a href="language.php?do=modify" target="_blank">Language Manager</a>.  If this language is just translated phrases and no custom settings then you can select "Yes" here.  Otherwise you should select "No" to keep the language whole as it is now.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
