(65537, -1, 'options_options_needfromemail_text', 'cphelptext', 'Some email servers require the "-f" parameter to be sent with email calls from PHP. If users are not receiving email from your forum, then you can try enabling this option.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
