(67047, -1, 'usergroup_add_edit_canhiderep_text', 'cphelptext', 'This permission allows the user to have the option, from their User CP, of not participating in the reputation system.  While the user can still receive reputation comments, their reputation will not be visible to other users.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1223482380, '4.0.0 Alpha 1', 0),
