(67251, -1, 'usertools_doips_depth_text', 'cphelptext', 'A depth setting of 1 will only return the results of the specified search.  A depth setting of 2 will return the results of the specified search, as well as running a search on each of the results.\r\n<br /><br />For example:<br /><br />\r\nA search on 127.0.0.1 with a depth of 1 returns "Freddie" and "Scott". A search on 127.0.0.1 with a depth setting of 2 returns "Freddie" and "Scott", as well as returning all of the ip addresses used by "Freddie" and "Scott".', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
